mage_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-9dcd848b255162cd0e39d01627967e5c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "97 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2051651172188911164"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI0oLRx8XV3tFxEAMaCTEyMDA2MzYzOSDtvdjRBjAAOBhADHITMjA1MTY1MTE3MjE4ODkxMTE2NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1782015301.273575", "card_id": "Q_2050875839395410256", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 45}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "余华称「报志愿理科我选数学，文科选哲学」，对当下高考志愿填报有借鉴意义吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "6 月 17 日，作家余华现身北京国际图书博览会特别访谈活动。正值高考志愿填报季，当被邀请分享志愿填报心得时，余华幽默自嘲，自己曾两次高考落榜，如今却身为北京师范大学教授，为考生解答志愿填报问题十分特别。 谈及理想志愿，他坦言，若重回十八岁填报志愿，理科会选择数学，文科则会选择哲学。余华表示，在多数人眼中，数学和哲学看似实用性不强、就业优势不明显，但他认为，两门学科是锤炼思维的最佳选择。数学是一切科学的基础，能搭建理科思维逻辑；而哲学可以塑造独特的认知眼光，构建完整的思维体系，让人拥有更开阔的视野，从容应对各类问题。余华支招高考志愿填报：偏爱看似「无用」的数学与哲学 - 中新网视频"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8ddfadd858c93b75dc5ff72d7e0463d1.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "83 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2050875839395410256"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI0oLRx8XV3tFxEAMaCTEyMDAzMTE2OSDXmc3RBjAAODhADXITMjA1MDg3NTgzOTM5NTQxMDI1NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1782015301.274365", "card_id": "EV_12222533", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 0}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "每天都吃各种不同的保健品，到底是会更健康，还是更可能提高肝肾损伤的风险？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "不吃，怕缺营养，吃，又怕有什么互相作用。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e9fe0131ec9adc3a5257cf5f41016f9e.jpg?source=2bcfc003"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "79 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color":